longBusinessSummary: Supreme Infrastructure India Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the engineering and construction of roads, highways, buildings, and bridges in India. It also engages in railways, power, water-infrastructure and drainage, and other projects. In addition, the company owns and operates ready mix concrete, wet mix plant, quarries, paver block unit, asphalt, and crushing plants. Supreme Infrastructure India Limited was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Mumbai, India.
